Creating Rolling Weeks Slicer 15

Choose the Slicer Visual, select the rolling weeks field

- Under visualization pane choose general

X position = 0, Y position = 89, Width = 189, Height = 93

- Title is on = Rolling Weeks, Font color = black, Font family = Constantia

- Background is on = Color = light blue (same throughout the project on the backgrounds)

- Border on = Color = dark gray (make sure all borders are the same color throughout the project)



More detail about  rolling average graph.
